{
  "Stoichiometry": "测量学",
  "This lesson covers the fundamental measures of center used to analyze and summarize data sets. You'll learn how to calculate and apply the mean, median, and mode, and understand when each is most appropriate.": "这个课程涵盖了分析和总结数据集的中心的基本测量方法。 您将学会如何计算和应用平均值、 中位数和模式, 并了解何时最合适 。",
  "What is Avogadro's number?": "阿沃加德罗的号码是多少?",
  "Avogadro's number (6.022 × 10²³) is the number of particles (atoms, molecules, or ions) in one mole of a substance. It connects the macroscopic and atomic scales.": "Avogadro的编号(6.022 × 1023)是物质一个摩尔的颗粒数(原子、分子或离子)。它连接了宏观和原子尺度。",
  "What is the molar mass of water (H₂O)?": "水的摩尔质量(H2O)是多少?",
  "The molar mass of H₂O = 2(1.01) + 16.00 = 18.02 g/mol. Each hydrogen contributes about 1.01 g/mol and oxygen contributes 16.00 g/mol.": "H2O = 2(1.01) + 16.00 = 18.02 克/摩尔的摩尔质量,每个氢大约贡献1.01克/摩尔,氧大约贡献16.00克/摩尔。",
  "What is the mass percent of oxygen in glucose (C₆H₁₂O₆, molar mass = 180.16 g/mol)?": "葡萄糖中的氧气百分比(C6H12O6,摩尔质量=180.16克/摩尔)是多少?",
  "Mass % of O = (6 × 16.00) / 180.16 × 100 = 96.00/180.16 × 100 = 53.3%. Six oxygen atoms contribute 96.00 g to the 180.16 g/mol molar mass.": "质量 O = (6 × 16.00) / 180.16 × 100 = 96.00/180.16 × 100 = 53.3% 。 6个氧原子向180.16 g/ mol 摩尔质量贡献96.00克。",
  "In the reaction 2Al + 3Cl₂ → 2AlCl₃, what is the mole ratio of Al to Cl₂?": "在反应 2Al + 3Cl2  2AlCl3中, Al 与 Cl2 的摩尔比是多少?",
  "The coefficients in the balanced equation directly give the mole ratio. For every 2 moles of Al, 3 moles of Cl₂ are needed, giving a 2:3 mole ratio.": "平衡方程式中的系数直接给出了摩尔比率。 对于每2个摩尔,需要3个摩尔(CC2),给出2:3摩尔(CC2)比率。",
  "A compound is found to contain 40.0% C, 6.7% H, and 53.3% O by mass. What is its empirical formula?": "一种化合物按质量计算含有40.0% C、6.7% H和53.3% O。其实验公式是什么?",
  "Converting to moles: C = 40.0/12.01 = 3.33, H = 6.7/1.01 = 6.63, O = 53.3/16.00 = 3.33. Dividing by the smallest (3.33): C:H:O = 1:2:1, giving CH₂O. Wait - rechecking: 6.63/3.33 = 1.99 ≈ 2, so empirical formula is CH₂O.": "转换成摩尔:C = 40.0/12.01 = 3.33, H = 6.1.1.01 = 6.63, O = 53.3/16.00 = 3.33。 最小的(3.33): C:H = 1. 2, 给予 CH2O。 等待 - 重新检查: 6.63/3.33 = 1.99 = 2, 所以实验公式是 CH2O 。",
  "If the empirical formula of a compound is CH₂O and its molar mass is 180 g/mol, what is the molecular formula?": "如果一种化合物的经验公式是CH2O,其摩尔质量为180克/摩尔,那么分子公式是什么?",
  "Empirical formula mass of CH₂O = 12 + 2 + 16 = 30 g/mol. Multiplier = 180/30 = 6. Molecular formula = (CH₂O)₆ = C₆H₁₂O₆ (glucose).": "CH2O = 12 + 2 + 16 = 30 克/摩尔;倍数器 = 180/30 = 6. 分子式 = (CH2O)6 = C6H12O6 (胶囊)。",
  "What is a 'mole' in chemistry?": "什么是化学中的\"摩尔\"?",
  "A mole is the SI unit for amount of substance, defined as exactly 6.02214076 × 10²³ elementary entities. It bridges atomic masses (amu) to laboratory masses (grams).": "摩尔是物质量的SI单位,确切定义为6.02214076×1023个基本实体,将原子质量(AMU)与实验室质量(克)连接起来。",
  "What is 'stoichiometry'?": "什么是“异构测量法”?",
  "Stoichiometry uses the mole ratios from balanced equations to calculate the amounts of reactants and products. It is the mathematical foundation for quantitative chemistry.": "斯托伊奇测量利用平衡方程的摩尔比率计算反应器和产品的数量。它是定量化学的数学基础。",
  "What is a 'molecular formula'?": "什么是“分子公式”?",
  "The molecular formula gives the actual number of each type of atom in one molecule. It is a whole-number multiple of the empirical formula and requires knowledge of the molar mass to determine.": "分子公式给出一个分子中每个原子类型的实际数量。它是经验公式的全数倍数,需要了解摩尔质量才能确定。",
  "What is 'mass percent composition'?": "什么是“质量百分比构成”?",
  "Mass percent composition tells what fraction of a compound's total mass is contributed by each element. It is calculated by dividing the total mass of each element by the molar mass of the compound.": "质量百分数成分表示化合物总质量的分数由每个元素组成。计算方法是将每个元素的总质量除以化合物的摩尔质量。",
  "What is a 'formula unit'?": "什么是“公式单位”?",
  "A formula unit is the simplest ratio of ions in an ionic compound. For NaCl, one formula unit consists of one Na⁺ and one Cl⁻. Ionic compounds don't form discrete molecules, so we use formula units.": "公式单位是离子在离子化合物中的最简单比例。 对于 NaCl 来说, 一个公式单位包括一个 Na+和一个 Cl-。 离子化合物不形成离散分子, 所以我们使用公式单位 。",
  "A forensic chemist analyzes an unknown white powder and determines it contains 52.14% C, 13.13% H, and 34.73% O by mass. She suspects it might be ethanol (C₂H₆O) or MTBE (C₅H₁₂O). What is the empirical formula, and which compound could it be?": "法医化学家分析未知的白色粉末,确定它含有52.14%的C、13.13%的H和34.73%的O质量。她怀疑它可能是乙醇(C2H6O)或MTBE(C5H12O ) 。 经验公式是什么? 哪种化合物?",
  "Converting to moles: C = 52.14/12.01 = 4.34, H = 13.13/1.008 = 13.02, O = 34.73/16.00 = 2.17. Dividing by 2.17: C₂H₆O₁. The empirical formula C₂H₆O matches ethanol.": "转换成摩尔:C = 52.14/12.01 = 4.34, H = 13.13/1.08 = 13.02, O = 34.73/16.00 = 2.17, 分之2. 17: C2H6O1. 实验公式 C2H6O 匹配乙醇。",
  "A mining company extracts copper from chalcopyrite (CuFeS₂). The ore sample contains 34.5% CuFeS₂ by mass. If they process 1000 kg of ore, what is the maximum mass of copper (63.55 g/mol) they can extract? (CuFeS₂ molar mass = 183.52 g/mol)": "采矿公司从铬复制石(CuFeS2)中提取铜,矿石样品按质量计含有34.5%的CuFeS2,如果加工1000公斤矿石,它们能提取的铜的最大质量(63.55克/摩尔)是多少? (CuFeS2 摩尔质量=183.52克/摩尔)",
  "Mass CuFeS₂ = 0.345 × 1000 = 345 kg. Mass fraction of Cu in CuFeS₂ = 63.55/183.52 = 0.3463. Mass Cu = 345 × 0.3463 = 119 kg maximum copper.": "Mass CuFeS2 = 0.345 × 1000 = 345公斤 CuFeS2 = 63.55/183.52 = 0.3463。Mass Cu = 345 × 0.3463 = 119公斤最大铜。",
  "A combustion analysis lab burns 0.255 g of an unknown organic compound and collects 0.561 g of CO₂ and 0.306 g of H₂O. The compound contains only C, H, and O. What is its empirical formula?": "燃烧分析实验室燃烧了0.255克未知有机化合物,收集0.561克CO2和0.306克H2O。 该化合物只含有C、H和O。 其经验公式是什么?",
  "Moles C = 0.561/44.01 = 0.01275 mol. Moles H = 2 × (0.306/18.02) = 0.03397 mol. Mass O = 0.255 - (0.01275×12.01) - (0.03397×1.008) = 0.0674 g; moles O = 0.0674/16.00 = 0.00421. Ratio C:H:O = 3.03:8.07:1 ≈ 3:8:1. Empirical formula: C₃H₈O.": "摩莱斯 C = 0.561/44.01 = 0.0175 mol. Moles H = 2 × (0.306/18.02) = 0.03397 mol. mass O = 0.255 - (0.01275x12.01) - (0.03397x1.08) = 0.0674 g; 摩尔 O = 0.0674/1.6.00 = 0.00421. 比率 C:O = 3.03:8.07:1 = 3:8:1. 经验式: C3H8O。"
}